name: spirit
description: six. has your computer ever malfunctioned inexplicably? those glitches that happen once and never again? most call them "bugs," but techno-savvy occultists know their true form: spirits. some are here to protect us, interrupting binary signals before we enter the wrong timeline. others are hungry ghosts, who demand attention and feed off our frustration. one cannot stop them, and only learn to work with them. collect to attract protection. inscribed by tenorless circa 2019 // genesis collection
